  (text "POWER NOTES (IPC-2221B / IPC-2152):\\n+5V_EXT: J4 barrel jack (CUI PJ-102AH 5.5/2.1mm tip-positive)\\n  → HUB75 panel direct (+5V_EXT_HUB75) and AMS1117-3.3 IN\\n  C1 100µF bulk + C2 100nF HF bypass at connector entry\\n  PCB trace: 1.5mm min (IPC-2152 3A 1oz Cu 10C rise outer layer)\\n+3V3: AMS1117-3.3 800mA rated ~400mA load 2x margin\\n  C3 10µF LDO input + C4 10µF LDO output + C5 100nF HF\\n  SOT-223 tab (pin2)=output. Thermal via array under tab min 4 vias.\\nLED indicators: D1 (5V 620Ω→5mA) D2 (3V3 270Ω→5mA)\\nAVDD (ES8388 analog): FB1 (BLM15AX601SN1D 600R@100MHz) from +3V3\\n  C6 10µF + C7 100nF on AVDD side of FB1 (analog island)\\nAGND/DGND star point: single net tie at U5 ES8388. See audio sheet."
    (at 20 80 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "ea474030-8255-41d7-a47a-87f7f25b5919")
  )
